1.0.0.name: is-typed-array
1.0.0.description: Check if the passed in object is a TypedArray (e.g. Float32Array).
1.0.0.deprecated: Please upgrade to v1.0.1 - v1.0.0 does not work in ES6 environments or across realms/iframes.

1.0.1.name: is-typed-array
1.0.1.description: Is this value a JS Typed Array? This module works cross-realm/iframe, does not depend on `instanceof` or mutable properties, and despite ES6 Symbol.toStringTag.
